{"tha-ap353:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap353:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap353:0.3":"Saddasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap353:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap353:1.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap353:1.3":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap353:1.4":"devasanghapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap353:2.1":"Catusaccam pakasentam, ","tha-ap353:2.2":"uddharantam mahajanam; ","tha-ap353:2.3":"Assosim madhuram vacam, ","tha-ap353:2.4":"karavikarudopamam. ","tha-ap353:3.1":"Brahmasarassa munino, ","tha-ap353:3.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap353:3.3":"Ghose cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap353:3.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap353:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap353:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap353:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap353:4.4":"pasadassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap353:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap353:5.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap353:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap353:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap353:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saddasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap353:7.1":"Saddasannakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}